Reason no one goes to VP anymore is the Risk vs Reward is crap.  VP is still on of the harder zones in the game due to the level of the mobs (60 min) the insane respawn time on these mobs (2 or 3 min?)  The dragons themselves aren't that hard cept for the sick AE's they have, 1200 DD ae on hosk and silverwing, and that damn stun AE Phara has.  And all of these dragons drop sub par gear, most of which has degraded to nothing more than toys for most players that are at a level that they can clear VP.<br>
<br>
Still VP is the BEST source of rare drop Kunark spells (sunstrike, malo, topor, pox, etc.) so if you want to go, camp your damn key like the rest of us, and start farming Trak for teeth (he drops like 2-4 every killing) VP key is a pain in the arse, but its nothing like SOL key quests <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  So stop bitching <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
